kmarkers<-classmarkers[rownames(classmarkers) %in% k$Gene.name & 
                         classmarkers$p_val_adj<0.05 & 
                         abs(classmarkers$avg_log2FC)>1,]
EnhancedVolcano(classmarkers,
                selectLab=rownames(kmarkers),
                lab=rownames(classmarkers),
                drawConnectors = T,
                pCutoff = 0.05,
